des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your VIVOHOME smart products in following few steps:
1. Download our “VIVOHOME” app in the App Store and then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in the “VIVOHOME” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “VIVOHOME” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can interact with Alexa to give her voice commands, such as: 
Alexa, turn on the plug.
Alexa, turn off the plug.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to green.
